moves.name: Absorb
moves.battle_effect: A GRASS-type attack. It adds half the HP it drained from the target to the attacker's HP.

moves.name: Acid
moves.battle_effect: A POISON-type attack. Has a one-in-ten chance of lowering the target's DEFENSE.

moves.name: Acid Armor
moves.battle_effect: Melts the user's body for protection. A move that sharply raises DEFENSE.

moves.name: Aeroblast
moves.battle_effect: A powerful FLYING-type attack. It often becomes a critical hit.

moves.name: Agility
moves.battle_effect: A special move that greatly boosts the user's SPEED. Normally used up to three times.

moves.name: Amnesia
moves.battle_effect: A move that increases the user's SPCL.DEF stat. It is normally used up to three times.

moves.name: AncientPower
moves.battle_effect: A ROCK-type attack. This prehistoric move may boost all of the user's stats.

moves.name: Attract
moves.battle_effect: Infatuates targets, making it hard for them to attack foes of the opposite gender.

moves.name: Aurora Beam
moves.battle_effect: An ICE-type attack. Has a  one-in-ten chance of reducing the target's ATTACK power.

moves.name: Barrage
moves.battle_effect: Several spheres are thrown consecutively at the target to inflict damage.
